readme: Improve this doc # Device ``` $ ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-device $ npm install --save @ionic-native/device ``` ## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/device/) Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/apache/cordova-plugin-device](https://github.com/apache/cordova-plugin-device) Access information about the underlying device and platform. ## Supported platforms - Android - Browser - iOS - macOS - Windows
